  <description>
  Doelan is an automated tool to check the quality of produced DNA
  microarrays. This software is based on the execution of parameted testsuites 
  on quality control data to validate batches of chips. This software will helps
  microarray platforms in their quality approach such as ISO 9001 certification.
  </description>
  
  <!-- a short description of what the project does -->
